These are Puzzles for 6x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, tea, water
There 7 different types of food: pineapple, potato, garlic, cranberry, asparagus, peas, zucchini
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, poppy, sunflower, begonia, azalea, zinnia
There are 7 different nationalities: british, canadian, egyptian, french, mexican, spanish, turkish
The people have 7 different jobs:  journalist, doctor, architect, firefighter, engineer, police-officer, analyst
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, scooter, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who growszinnia is the person driving the train##1
 2. the architect is on the left of the french##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 4. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the french is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person eating potato is the canadian##1
11. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the journalist is the person eating zucchini##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is between the firefighter and the doctor##2
14. the mexican is on the right of the engineer##1
15. the person drinking water is the person who growsazalea##1
16. the canadian is on the far right##1
17. the person eating garlic is on the left of the canadian##1
18. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating asparagus##1
19. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
20. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
21. the egyptian is on the right of the mexican##1
22. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
23. the mexican is in the middle##1
24. the spanish is the person drinking juice##1
25. the person driving the subway is on the right of the engineer##1
26. the person drinking juice is on the left of the police-officer##1
27. the person who growsdahlia is the turkish##1
28. the doctor is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
29. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
30. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
